magro 1.0
23 oct 2009
README
===========

This is a python module for evaluating templates in the
magro language. It uses a very easy to learn syntax designed
for great reuse and legibility.


Dependencies
------------
This module should work with Python 2.5+ but not yet
with Python 3+.

Requires the ply library, which can be found at:
http://www.dabeaz.com/ply/


Installation
------------
You can install this package using easy_install:

    easy_install magro

Or if you have downloaded the .tar.gz archive:

    tar xzvf magro-1.0.tar.gz
    cd magro-1.0
    python setup.py install


